<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-3061] Open IndexWriter API to allow custom MergeScheduler implementation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-3061</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;IndexWriter&apos;s getNextMerge() and merge(OneMerge) are package-private, which makes it impossible for someone to implement his own MergeScheduler. We should open up these API, as well as any other that can be useful for custom MS implementations.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
            <key id="12505914">LUCENE-3061</key>
            <summary>Open IndexWriter API to allow custom MergeScheduler implementation</summary>
